Class KeyQueuedExecutorService<K>

java.lang.Object
com.fastasyncworldedit.core.util.task.KeyQueuedExecutorService<K>
Type Parameters:
K - Key type
public class KeyQueuedExecutorService<K> extends Object
Executor service that queues tasks based on keys, executing tasks on a configurable ThreadPoolExecutor
